body: Yes. We just recently published a solution for this. iOS devices using Apple's latest A12 chips (i.e. iPhone XS and XR) achieve about 10-15 FPS with full YOLOv3 running at 416 pixels. App tested on iPhone XS, results on other hardware may differ.
